summary: An Ordinance accepting a quit-claim deed from Charles H. Cobb and Carrie B. Cobb, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 13th day of August, A. D. 1907, to a certain portion of Tracts 101-102 and 114 Replat of John J. McGilvra's Addition to the City of Seattle, and Blocks 13, 14, 18, 20 to 29 inclusive and south one half of 19 of John J. McGilvra's Second Addition to the City of Seattle.
